{"id": 7847, "source": "pestle", "subject": "chemistry", "course": null, "level": "SL", "paper": "1", "year": "2020", "session": "20N", "subtopic": "4-1-ionic-bonding-and-structure", "title": "20N.1.SL.TZ0.9", "topic_id": "4", "source_url": "https://pestle.pages.dev/app/", "question_html": "<div class=\"question\">\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Which formula is correct?</span></p>\n<p>A.  <math class=\"wrs_chemistry\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>NH</mi><mn>4</mn></msub><msub><mi>PO</mi><mn>4</mn></msub></math></p>\n<p>B.  <math class=\"wrs_chemistry\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mfenced><msub><mi>NH</mi><mn>4</mn></msub></mfenced><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi>PO</mi><mn>4</mn></msub></math></p>\n<p>C.  <math class=\"wrs_chemistry\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mfenced><msub><mi>NH</mi><mn>4</mn></msub></mfenced><mn>3</mn></msub><msub><mi>PO</mi><mn>4</mn></msub></math></p>\n<p>D.  <math class=\"wrs_chemistry\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mfenced><msub><mi>NH</mi><mn>4</mn></msub></mfenced><mn>3</mn></msub><msub><mfenced><msub><mi>PO</mi><mn>4</mn></msub></mfenced><mn>2</mn></msub></math></p>\n</div>", "solution_html": "<div class=\"question\">\n<p>C</p>\n</div>", "examiners_html": "<div class=\"question\">\n<p>64% of candidates picked the correct formula for ammonium phosphate with (NH<sub>4</sub>)<sub>2</sub>PO<sub>4</sub> being the incorrect answer chosen most frequently. NH<sub>4</sub>PO<sub>4</sub> or (NH<sub>4</sub>)<sub>3</sub>(PO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>2</sub> was rarely selected.</p>\n</div>"}